        Parameters:
        length - The length of the AD structure.
        type - The AD type. The value should always be 0x16 (Service Data - 16-bit UUID).
        data - The AD data whose format is Eddystone. The first two bytes should be 0xAA and 0xFE.
        frameType - The frame type.
